@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Home Page";
}

<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="hero" style="">
    <div class="container">
        <br><br>
        <h1>Trail<br>Running<br>With Jake!</h1>
        <div style="background-color: var(--primary); margin-top: 8px; width: 100px; height: 8px; margin-bottom: 10px; transform: scale(1, 1); visibility: visible;" data-width="10px" data-animate="yes" data-animation-delay="" data-color="accent-color" class="divider-small-border completed"></div>
        <p>Join the Trail Running with Jake club today!</p>
        <div class="hero-buttons">
            <a href="/Home/Join" class=" hero-buttons button button-primary">Join Now</a>
            <a href="/Home/Join" class="hero-buttons button button-outline">Personal Training</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="features vests">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="vest-flex-container">
            <div class="vest-text-column">
                <h2>All About Jake</h2>
                <p class="highlight-text">Jake's journey has been shaped by passion, dedication, and a deep desire to make a positive impact in the world. Growing up, he was always drawn to the outdoors and the power of nature. His love for trail running became more than just a hobby; it became a way of connecting with others and promoting a healthy lifestyle. As an advocate for the environment, Jake strives to inspire others to not only embrace nature but also to take part in initiatives that help those in need.</p>
                <p class="highlight-text">Through his passion for outdoor activities, Jake became involved in numerous community projects. One of his proudest achievements is working to provide those in need with practical solutions, like the high-tech foam vests that help keep people warm in extreme conditions. Jake’s mission is to raise awareness about important causes while fostering a community of compassion and action. By sharing his love for running and his commitment to social responsibility, Jake is making a difference in the lives of others, one step at a time.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="vest-image-column">
                <img class="feature-image" src="images/mount_timp.JPG"/>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="features paragraph-section">
    <div class="container faq">
        <h1 style="color: white;">About Trails With Jake...</h1>
        <div class="features-grid">
            <div class="feature-card">
                <h3 class="mt-3">Run Club</h3>
                <p>Join the Trail Running with Jake Run Club, where you'll experience the thrill of running through some of the most scenic trails around the country. Whether you're a seasoned runner or just starting, our club provides the support and motivation you need to stay on track, improve your fitness, and have fun along the way. Come for the trails, stay for the community!</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <h3 class="mt-3">Personal Training</h3>
                <p>Take your fitness to the next level with personalized training tailored to your goals. With Jake’s expert guidance, you'll get a customized training plan that focuses on your strengths and helps you improve your endurance, speed, and trail running skills. Whether you're preparing for an event or just want to stay fit, we’ll help you reach your full potential.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

